author: maintainer-agent
estimated_minutes: 60
acceptance_criteria: "Unknown --status on list errors with the valid domain (including configured statuses); behavior consistent with search status: validator; regression tests for list/list-* variants; GH-530 closed"
parent: pm-mpbb
risk: low
confidence: high
resolution: Resolved by enabling strict runtime status-registry parsing for list filters.
expected_result: Unknown statuses fail with the configured status domain instead of returning a false empty result.
actual_result: "Unknown list status returns usage exit 2 while built-in, workflow, and custom aliases remain supported."
